              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <blockquote class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
            " A few features were missing, but it's looking promising. Looking
            forward to how it looks like in a year's time! "
          </blockquote>
          <div class="font-red-hat-display font-bold mt-2">
            <cite class="not-italic">—Edmund Clarke</cite>
          </div>
        </div>

